409
00:26:26.166 --> 00:26:27.501
Sabay tayong maghapunan.

410
00:26:27.876 --> 00:26:29.253
Binibigyan mo ako ng kilabot.

411
00:26:29.336 --> 00:26:31.839
Samahan mo akong kumain,
